### Cache Increment API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000

### Health Check
GET {{host}}/api/counter/health

###

### Increment Counter - Simple
POST {{host}}/api/counter/page_views/increment

###

### Increment Counter - With Custom Amount
POST {{host}}/api/counter/page_views/increment?incrementBy=5

###

### Get Counter Value from Redis
GET {{host}}/api/counter/page_views

###

### Get Counter Value from MySQL (Force Database)
GET {{host}}/api/counter/page_views?forceFromDatabase=true

###

### Set Counter to Specific Value
PUT {{host}}/api/counter/page_views
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": 1000
}

###

### Check Sync Status
GET {{host}}/api/counter/page_views/sync-status

###

### Manual Sync to MySQL
POST {{host}}/api/counter/page_views/sync

###

### Get All Counters from MySQL
GET {{host}}/api/counter/mysql/all

###

### Test Multiple Counters
POST {{host}}/api/counter/user_logins/increment

###

POST {{host}}/api/counter/api_calls/increment?incrementBy=3

###

POST {{host}}/api/counter/downloads/increment?incrementBy=10

###

### Rapid Fire Test (increment same counter multiple times)
POST {{host}}/api/counter/rapid_test/increment

###

POST {{host}}/api/counter/rapid_test/increment

